&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Windlinxy/Typora-img/main/img/image-20220423105408450.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20220423105408450&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
